<text x="10" y="20" color="yellow" backgroundColor="black" form="bold/underline">Rule of the game:</text>
<text x="10" y="22" color="blue" backgroundColor="black">The purpose of the game is to evolve in a donjon, to collect chests</text>
<text x="10" y="23" color="blue" backgroundColor="black">to improve your weapons and make them more powerful to overcome</text>
<text x="10" y="24" color="blue" backgroundColor="black">monsters without dying.</text>

<text x="10" y="26" color="light blue" backgroundColor="black">Also you only have one life, once you die and you leave the</text>
<text x="10" y="27" color="light blue" backgroundColor="black">dungeon. When you want to replay, it will not be anymore</text>
<text x="10" y="28" color="light blue" backgroundColor="black">the same donjon.</text>

<text x="10" y="30" color="blue" backgroundColor="black">In every dungeon, there will be a boss. If you manage </text>
<text x="10" y="31" color="blue" backgroundColor="black">to defeat him, you will go one level. You will reach</text>
<text x="10" y="32" color="blue" backgroundColor="black">then another longer and more difficult donjon.</text>

<text x="10" y="34" color="yellow" backgroundColor="black" form="bold/underline">How to play:</text>
<text x="10" y="36" color="light blue" backgroundColor="black">To move in the donjon and execute the actions of the personage,</text>
<text x="10" y="37" color="light blue" backgroundColor="black">press once the touch indicated in the menu options.</text>

